OL,3,C'They were less than human': Britain's
OL,4,Cforced adoption scandal
OL,6,F"The archbishops talked about saving
OL,7,Fcatholic souls, the saving the soul
OL,8,Fwas more important than saving the
OL,9,Flife," she said. "They viewed it as
OL,10,Fonce they were in the institution,
OL,11,Fthey were less than human."
OL,13,FFiona Cahill is campaigning for
OL,14,Fcompensation from both Irish and
OL,15,FBritish governments over the treatment
OL,16,Fof her mother and grandmother
OL,18,FShe has spent decades examining
OL,19,Farchives and files trying to piece
OL,20,Ftogether the mysteries of her mother's
OL,21,Fchildhood.
