OL,3,C'They were less than human': Britain's
OL,4,Cforced adoption scandal
OL,6,F"She'd struggle controlling her
OL,7,Femotions," she said. "It could be
OL,8,Fchaotic and difficult growing up. We
OL,9,Fjust had to try to support her, but I
OL,10,Fjust remember feeling helpless."
OL,12,FMaria who lived in Doncaster and
OL,13,Fpassed away in 2023 aged 69, only
OL,14,Ffound out she was adopted when she was
OL,15,F21 as she applied for a passport.
OL,17,FIt wasn't until she was 40 that she
OL,18,Fdiscovered she was a British citizen
OL,19,Fafter finding out that she had two
OL,20,Fbirth certificates, a UK one and a
OL,21,F"falsified" Irish one.
