OL,3,C'They were less than human': Britain's
OL,4,Cforced adoption scandal
OL,6,FIn the decades that followed she tried
OL,7,Funsuccessfully to trace her birth
OL,8,Fparents.
OL,10,F"All she ever wanted was a hug from
OL,11,Fher own mum," Fiona said.
OL,13,FSince her mother's death, Fiona feels
OL,14,Fit's her duty to carry on the campaign
OL,15,Ffor justice and recognition. "It's
OL,16,Flike a dark corner that never goes
OL,17,Faway," she added.
