OL,3,C'They were less than human': Britain's
OL,4,Cforced adoption scandal
OL,6,FIn March, Labour MP Liam Conlon, who
OL,7,Fis the national chair of the Labour
OL,8,FParty Irish Society, introduced
OL,9,FPhilomena's Law to support the 13,000
OL,10,Fsurvivors of Ireland's mother and baby
OL,11,Fhomes in Britain.
OL,13,FSpeaking to ITV News, Mr Conlon said
OL,14,Fhe had been "unaware" of the PFI
OL,15,Fforced repatriation scheme and
OL,16,Fdescribed it as "horrific".
OL,18,F"It's really shocking and a really
OL,19,Funderreported and unrecognised aspect
OL,20,Fof this wider scandal," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
