OL,3,C'They were less than human': Britain's
OL,4,Cforced adoption scandal
OL,6,F"To hear that women who would have
OL,7,Fbeen very vulnerable, who would have
OL,8,Fcome here (to Britain) to then be
OL,9,Fdeported, often very pregnant, and put
OL,10,Fin those institutions is horrific."
OL,12,F'People want truth on the record',
OL,13,FLabour MP Liam Conlon, who is the
OL,14,Fnational chair of the Labour Party
OL,15,FIrish Society, told ITV News
OL,17,FFiona and her family are now calling
OL,18,Ffor all archives from religious and
OL,19,Fstate run mother and baby institutions
OL,20,Fin the UK to be preserved and
OL,21,Faccessible.
