OL,3,C'They were less than human': Britain's
OL,4,Cforced adoption scandal
OL,6,FShe wants a special site to house
OL,7,Fdocuments, objects and oral history,
OL,8,Fso that this dreadful period of
OL,9,Fhistory cannot be forgotten.
OL,11,F"There are many people who still
OL,12,Fassume they were 'given up' and remain
OL,13,Ftotally unaware of the manner in which
OL,14,Funmarried women and children were
OL,15,Ftreated," Fiona added.
OL,17,FIn 2021 the Irish Taoiseach delivered
OL,18,Fa formal apology for historic forced
OL,19,Fadoption and the suffering caused.
