OL,3,C'They were less than human': Britain's
OL,4,Cforced adoption scandal
OL,6,FIn response to our investigation, the
OL,7,FUK government said: "This abhorrent
OL,8,Fpractice should never have taken
OL,9,Fplace, and our deepest sympathies are
OL,10,Fwith all those affected.
OL,12,F"We take this issue extremely
OL,13,Fseriously and continue to engage with
OL,14,Fthose impacted to provide support."
OL,16,FIn 2016 the head of the Catholic
OL,17,FChurch in England and Wales apologised
OL,18,F"for the hurt caused by agencies
OL,19,Facting in the name of the Catholic
OL,20,FChurch".
